{
  "stem": "22889.4",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I slept in the barracks number 18 in Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He used to bring meat, used to help us out-- his close friends.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He took care of his dogs, Goeth's dogs-- he had a bunch of dogs.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I never forget-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] when they brought a guy-- he tried to escape, a young fellow.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They brought him into Krakow-Plaszow, and the whole camp-- the whole population together-- watch him hang, to be hang.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So they had-- we all watch, stand and watch him.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "First time they hang him, the rope broke, fell down.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Three times, the rope broke down, they couldn't hang him.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Finally he got so mad, Goeth, himself, took the pistol and-- when the rope broke down, he fell down, he shot him right there.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "This was incident.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Second time I remember, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] we had a-- the fellow who used to-- the engineer, they called engineer, he would set up the plan to where to put up the barracks.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "His name was Krakauer, a Jewish fellow.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he had a group with him, they used to work with him.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He was the engineer.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He was setting up the plans.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Krakauer, he was older man.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And after the camps was finished almost, he brought all the groups-- his group-- to Commander Goeth.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "He didn't like something, it was they did wrong.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They put them in a circle, hold each other.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "There were a bunch of them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They brought the steam shovel, they buried them alive in Plaszow-- right by the [NON-ENGLISH] station down there.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
